description: Spreading the flavors of New Mexico far and wide, 505 Food Truck LA is adding some serious spice to your life.Featuring the finest in red and green chiles from all over New Mexico, everything on this menu is sure to show your taste buds a great time. The glorious Green Chile Mac and Cheese Balls will satisfy your hunger, the Red Chile Beef will leave you breathless, and their exquisite New Mexico-style Enchiladas are just out of this world! New Mexico soul and California love have combined to create an amazing food truck you just can't miss.
name: 505 Food Truck LA
